### Documentation Strategy
- **docs/** â†’ Project-wide documentation (AI disclosure, architecture notes)
- **tests/** â†’ Each test module has matching `.md` explaining its purpose
- **conftest.md** â†’ Documentation for the test framework itself  

This ensures the entire system is self-explaining.

